	<Paragraph>The Omea application core only provides the basic infrastructure. All of the functionality is contributed by various plugins, for example, RSS feeds support is brought by the RSS Plugin.</Paragraph>
	<Paragraph>Plugins communicate with the application core through the Open API. The same interface is available to built-in plugins and third-party plugins.</Paragraph>
	<Paragraph>Plugin creation is documented on Omea Wiki.</Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>
